<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Dampit Trans - Password Reset</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top-left-radius: 10px;
      border-top-right-radius: 10px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .logo {
      max-width: 100px;
      height: auto;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .reset-button {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Password Reset</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <img src="https://bangteg.github.io/images/dampit-trans-logo.png" alt="Dampit Trans Logo" class="logo">
      <p>Dear <%= firstName %>,</p>
      <p>You have requested a password reset for your Dampit Trans Solo account. Please click the button below to reset your password:</p>
      <a href="<%= path %>/<%= token %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="reset-button">Reset Password</a>
      <p><strong>Note:</strong> This link will expire in 15 minutes for security reasons.</p>
      <p>If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:cs-dampit@gmail.com">cs-dampit@gmail.com</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p><b>Dampit Trans Solo</b></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>